# Text Editor Project
A sophisticated text processing system with modular design and robust error handling.

## Creator & Contributors
Dzorbaar from zone01 Athens - Original Creator
Phind - AI Assistant & Model

## Features
- Line-by-line file processing
- Multiple text modification capabilities
- Comprehensive error handling
- Clean code organization
- Modular design for easy extension

## Project Structure
```plaintext
text_editor/
├── main.go
├── text_editor.go
├── write.go
├── display.go
├── README.md
└── go.mod
```

## Usage
```bash
go run main.go
```

## Input/Output Files
- Input file: 

- Output file: 


## Text Modifications
The editor supports multiple text modifications:
- Hex to decimal conversion
- Binary to decimal conversion
- Case modifications
- Punctuation normalization
- Apostrophe standardization
- Article capitalization

## Error Handling
The system implements comprehensive error handling:
- File operation errors
- Text processing errors
- Resource cleanup on error
- Detailed error logging

## Contributing
Contributions are welcome! Please submit pull requests with:
- Clear commit messages
- Updated documentation
- Additional test cases

